  {
    "id": "43075288",
    "title": "TO REVIEW - Weisshorn V3.0 | 25.08 | Sprint 1 (master, release/weisshorn_v3.0)",
    "url": "https://confluence-secutix.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/RN/pages/43075288",
    "status": "current",
    "version": 2,
    "created": "",
    "updated": "2024-10-21T02:52:38.120Z",
    "text": "New features \n\n [STX-123176]\u00a0CHANGE-811 MYT As an operator, I can config to disable option to print as e-ticket if purchased with Mobile shipment mode \n\n [STX-123554]\u00a0Fixed price season card - the basics (Core) \n\n A new type of season tickets, called fixed price season card, allows your customer to buy a card of X matches inside a championship (for example 5 matches for a 19 matches championship) and select the matches in a later step. [championship, seasoncard, seasonticket] \n\n [STX-123016]\u00a0[FIFASTX-3092] - Multi-currency support for Ticket Cancellation Insurance with Percentage Only - Service adaptation \n\n You can now define new level prices using gradient. See \"How to configure a cancellation insurance\" guide (https://confluence.secutix.com/wiki/display/RN/How+to+configure+a+cancellation+insurance) . [Back-office, CancellationInsurance] \n\n [STX-124310]\u00a0As an operator, I can see that the total net amount for products with price break down is calculated in such way that the rounding impact is minimum \n\n [STX-123827]\u00a0[FIFASTX-3219] FIFAT - Tickets on resale appear on to wrong sales channel \n\n [STX-120572]\u00a0Ticketshop: update jquery version \n\n [STX-119735]\u00a0[CHANGE-211] Define a default number of days (after reservation and before product date) for reservation payment deadline (p2) \n\n Currently the reservation deadline are set at product level in the catalog. This new feature will let you define reservation deadline at season level and product level making it much simpler to manage your reservation and booking policies. [Back-office, batch, reservation] \n\n [STX-123186]\u00a0CHANGE-922 RBL - E-commerce tracking / GTM \n\n N/A \n\n [STX-119652]\u00a0CHANGE-770 OnP - In the menu catalog and performance add two filter one by site and one by space \n\n The list of performances screen has 2 new filters to let you search and manage the performance more efficiently. [Back-office, seatmap] \n\n [STX-122727]\u00a0[FIFASTX-3049] [MTDS] GS portal - improvement of the ticket injection mechanism \n\n [STX-122726]\u00a0[FIFASTX-2807] [Documents] - Ticket sorting by Block/Row/Seat \n\n NA. See RN of STX-122725 [B2C, document, ticketshop] \n\n [STX-122725]\u00a0[FIFASTX-2807] [All Shops] - Ticket sorting by Block/Row/Seat \n\n [STX-124605]\u00a0[FIFASTX-2807] [Documents] Missing points \n\n NA. See RN of STX-122725 [B2C, document, ticketshop] \n\n [STX-122101]\u00a0AWS Prometheus service \n\n [STX-124175]\u00a0Prisma direct integration - set-up test environment \n\n [STX-123261]\u00a0[Italy] As a system, I can see the parent movement information on file detail Ticketshop \n\n N/A \n\n [STX-123148]\u00a0UEFASTX3-336 Adapt ITR to export necessary data for the TMT distribution map details section. \n\n [STX-123469]\u00a0New API to get seat availability with pagination \n\n [STX-123183]\u00a0CHANGE-797 FFC As operator, I can configure at screen Social Network to declare the cookie that determine user has logged in at main site \n\n [STX-123292]\u00a0CHANGE-827 Configure termination website \n\n [STX-123191]\u00a0CHANGE-641 TOM Cashdesk opening management (financed) \n\n You can now prevent cashiers from opening when receiving payment with a credit card. The feature can be enabled with the help of your customer success agent. \n\n [STX-120098]\u00a0Online Sales quantum should use the widget from legacy S3 \n\n [STX-120133]\u00a0Implement 3D Secure V2 with AndersonZaks - Step 1 \n\n [STX-123151]\u00a0UEFASTX3-335 TMT user flow correction during map pre-distribution. \n\n N/A \n\n [STX-121252]\u00a0Auto-close unused products in current seasons #2 \n\n [STX-123257]\u00a0CHANGE-582 CD44 Make Pass visit Package with conditional condition \n\n When you are offering Packages as a type of product on your ticket shop, you can now set the alert for the potential selection of overlapping events. The alert will notify the ticket shop user that at least one of the events they selected is overlapping. This action will give a ticket shop user a chance to correct the selection. \n\n [STX-123253]\u00a0CHANGE-891 ONP Deselect seat by click on seat in Widget Seatmap \n\n User interaction improvement that will let users click to unselect seat on the seatmap selection widget. [online, seatmap] \n\n [STX-123252]\u00a0CHANGE-891 ONP Deselect seat by click on seat in Online Seatmap \n\n User interaction improvement that will let users click to unselect seat on the seatmap selection screen online. [online, seatmap] \n\n [STX-119390]\u00a0[CHANGE-228] Implement a user friendly and configurable payment page - Ticket Shop \n\n Customise the payment method selection page directly from the SecuTix back-end. For example, you can decide how the methods should be grouped and add descriptions to be displayed to your internet users. [payment, ticketshop] \n\n [STX-122307]\u00a0CHANGE-252 As an internet user, without explicit consent, I only have limited access to my F&F contact \n\n In order to improve the data privacy, a new consent process has been added to the Friends&Family feature. We strongly advise you to enable this consent process if you use the Friends&Family feature. Read more (https://go.confluence.secutix.com/wiki/spaces/RN/pages/43058550/Request+explicit+consent+to+use+the+Friends+Family+feature) [GDPR, friendsandfamily] \n\n [STX-122105]\u00a0Cybersource COL - Creating new plugin variant \n\n [STX-123552]\u00a0As a quantum factory user, I can leverage self service infrastructure to manage ECR repositories for my cell \n\n [STX-122951]\u00a0Technical upgrades \n\n [STX-121323]\u00a0[Stabilization] Enable code coverage reports \n\n [STX-117857]\u00a0[Performance] getOrderDataForLockedSeats is extremely slow where then are many locks \n\n [STX-114206]\u00a0Various NPE in TnSEB module \n\n [STX-120678]\u00a0DistributionPublicServiceInternalImpl::updateDistributionHistoryForFailTakeBackTicket performance issue \n\n [STX-119129]\u00a0Call https://someticket.shop.secutix.com/status to get alive information \n\n [STX-123287]\u00a0[Data Migration] Data Import Package 22-Q2 \n\n [STX-122570]\u00a0[Stablization][Gravity] Adapt properly redux for widgets - Donation + Contact Origin \n\n [STX-123009]\u00a0Switch to paper: multiple screens appear \n\n [STX-120614]\u00a0Improvement for Fundraising Dashboard and Business Indicator Batch \n\n [STX-122791]\u00a0Stabilization actions \n\n Bug fixes \n\n [STX-124528]\u00a0Payment value date in the future \n\n [STX-124848]\u00a0Report rebuild of HUB KO \n\n [STX-124850]\u00a0Tickets appear as duplicated when customer tries to resell them and refund shows incorrect / double amount \n\n [STX-124948]\u00a0FIFA PASS interface not retrieving refunds correctly \n\n [STX-125020]\u00a0Orders created in Skidata DTA without consumerCategoryId, which is mandatory-non-mandatory field \n\n Additional bug fixes \n\n [STX-124347]\u00a0The alert message format for closing the cash desk is not the correct one \n\n [STX-124352]\u00a0FWC22 | Missing gray overlay for currently unavailable matches on the match selection page \n\n [STX-124427]\u00a0Labels one-click can't keep the change \n\n [STX-124435]\u00a0Not understandable DE translation in the cash desk closure report \n\n [STX-124566]\u00a0Spelling error in payment cancelation window in OL \n\n [STX-124832]\u00a0Missing translations for button Resell tickets \n\n [STX-123061]\u00a0LVAN - SAGE interface - INTRACO VAT sales no longer flow to the correct account \n\n [STX-123404]\u00a0Predefined SSTK : Can buy ticket no exceeding number of authorized tickets configured \n\n [STX-123970]\u00a0LVAN - SAGE interface -Structures whose relays are moved are not exported. \n\n [STX-124083]\u00a0Import of contacts, contacts are not usable \n\n [STX-124091]\u00a0TED Dashboard events out of order (Date) once more products button is clicked \n\n [STX-124105]\u00a0Word \"address\" in the shipment area has not been translated (should be German and not English) \n\n [STX-124127]\u00a0Movements Cannot Be Created for a File \n\n [STX-124340]\u00a0Wrong translation (wording needs to be corrected in Ticketshop) \n\n [STX-124440]\u00a0Template editor printer is not working \n\n [STX-124489]\u00a0Webhook access control sending check KO tickets \n\n [STX-124498]\u00a0Webhook refunds not included and barcodes missed \n\n [STX-124593]\u00a0CLONE - Boutique purchase current season",
    "content_size": 10422,
    "text_size": 7892
  }
]